              "settings": {
                "text": "<p>Viti Vinci is led by founder and creative director Victor Alarcón. His work is grounded in belief that perfumery can exist as an artistic discipline - one that engages with culture, ecology and human perception. </p><p>Drawing from both traditional perfumery and contemporary art, his approch combines material knowledge with conceptual thinking, shaping a practice where scent becomes a way of exploring identity, place and transformation.</p>",
